---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  keywords="board advisory services UK, non-executive director, strategic consultant, executive coaching, board governance, NED recruitment, organizational wellbeing, FCMI Fellow, IoD Ambassador"
  title="Craig Fearn - Strategic Consultant | Board Advisory | Executive Leadership"
  description="Strategic consultant specializing in board advisory and AI-enhanced decision-making. FCMI Fellow | FRSPH Fellow | IoD Ambassador. 17 years of board-level experience."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-brand-800 text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <!-- Main Headline -->
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
            The Strategic Advisor Boards Turn to First
          </h1>

          <!-- Supporting Copy -->
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-100 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Most consultants have frameworks. Craig has boardroom scars. Combine 17 years of director-level experience with Fellowship-level expertise for advice that actually works in the real world.
          </p>

          <!-- Credentials Bar -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-200">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full">IoD Ambassador</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full">FRSPH Fellow</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full">FCMI Fellow</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full">IoD Awards Finalist 2025</span>
          </div>

          <!-- CTA Buttons -->
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
            <Button href="/contact" size="large">
              Book a Strategy Call
            </Button>
            <Button href="/services" variant="secondary" size="large">
              Explore Services
            </Button>
          </div>

          <!-- Trust Indicators -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 text-sm text-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>100+ Organizations Supported</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>NHS, FTSE & Tech Sectors</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>IoD Awards Finalist 2025</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Craig's Image -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block">
          <img
            src="/images/iod-conference-142.jpg"
            alt="Craig Fearn at IoD Conference"
            class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
            width="800"
            height="1105"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Proposition Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Strategic Advisory When Stakes Are High
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          When you need strategic clarity—not generic advice—you need someone who's navigated the same challenges. Board governance. Executive pressure. Organizational complexity. Cultural transformation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Craig has led through it, not just studied it. 17 years at board level across NHS, technology, financial services, and professional services. IoD Ambassador, FRSPH Fellow, FCMI Fellow—specialized guidance that draws on both deep experience and evidence-based methodology.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Service 1: Board Advisory -->
        <div class="card p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Board Advisory & Governance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Navigate complex board dynamics, governance challenges, and strategic decisions. Get clarity from someone who's chaired the meetings and made the calls.
          </p>
          <a href="/services/board-advisory" class="text-primary font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 transition-colors">
            Learn more →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2: Executive Coaching -->
        <div class="card p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Executive Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Develop leadership capability with coaching that combines psychological insight, strategic thinking, and real-world board-level experience.
          </p>
          <a href="/services/executive-coaching" class="text-secondary font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 transition-colors">
            Learn more →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3: Organizational Wellbeing -->
        <div class="card p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Organizational Wellbeing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Understand organizational wellbeing with human-AI analysis that surfaces patterns invisible to traditional surveys. Strategic insights that connect wellbeing to performance.
          </p>
          <a href="/services/wellbeing-audit" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 transition-colors">
            Learn more →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credentials Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Experience That Can't Be Googled
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Most strategic advisors have qualifications. Some have experience. Very few have both at this level.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <img
                src="/images/RSPH-Fellow-Badge.jpg"
                alt="FRSPH Fellow Badge"
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                width="150"
                height="150"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 text-gray-900 mb-2">FRSPH Fellow</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Royal Society for Public Health</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <img
                src="/images/IoD-Ambassador-badge-web.png"
                alt="IoD Ambassador Badge"
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                width="150"
                height="150"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 text-gray-900 mb-2">IoD Ambassador</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Institute of Directors South West</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <img
                src="/images/iod-aspiring-award-badge.png"
                alt="IoD Aspiring Director Award"
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                width="150"
                height="150"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 text-gray-900 mb-2">IoD Awards Finalist</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Aspiring Director 2025</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <img
                src="/images/iod-global-award-badge.png"
                alt="IoD Global Award"
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                width="150"
                height="150"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 text-gray-900 mb-2">IoD Global Award</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Finalist 2025</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FCMI Credential Below -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold">
            FCMI Fellow | Chartered Management Institute
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-4">
          What Directors Say
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Trusted by board-level leaders across sectors
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Testimonial 1: Steve Hill (IoD Chair) -->
        <div class="card p-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "As an Ambassador for the IoD, Craig has started and sustained a local IoD member networking group. This group has been meeting monthly for almost two years now. An excellent achievement. He has also built strong engagements with local authorities and other local groups."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Steve Hill</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">IoD Chair</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 2: Andrew Honey -->
        <div class="card p-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "Craig is an absolute workhorse, with a mission to change lives through better governance and a real understanding of what wellbeing means. Craig helps Directors improve overall business performance by making people matter."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Andrew Honey CDir FIoD</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">NED / Consultant</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 3: Richard Sharpe -->
        <div class="card p-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "What truly sets Craig apart is his extensive knowledge, continued deep empathy and practical results-driven approach. His integrity makes him an invaluable asset to any individual or organization he supports."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Richard Sharpe</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">C-Suite Operational Board Leader</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-brand-800 text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold mb-6">
          Start with a Conversation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-100 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          No pressure. No sales pitch. Just a strategic conversation about your challenge. Most clients start with a 45-minute exploratory call to discuss what they're navigating and whether Craig's experience and approach are the right fit.
        </p>
        <Button href="/contact" size="large" variant="secondary">
          Book a Strategy Call
        </Button>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-200 mt-4">
          All conversations are confidential and obligation-free.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
